Package edu.sru.group3.WebBasedEvaluations.domain

Class Group

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.group3.WebBasedEvaluations.domain.Group
@Entity public class Group extends Object
Groups class creates a group for evaluation the id is used to id identify the group Class variables to state if a group evaluation have stared or if self evaluation are needed Class variables to determine what Evaluation template the group is using has a list of reviewee and evaluators. and able to append to the lists
